(32, 1, '2016-02-11 22:40:41', '2016-02-11 22:40:41', 'Freeform Portland is a 501(3)c nonprofit organization benefiting our community through providing a number of public resources:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Broadcasting Musicology classes</li>\r\n	<li>Music library</li>\r\n	<li>Promoting local music and arts events</li>\r\n	<li>More!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur station runs on volunteer and financial support from our friends and neighbors and we are grateful for any and all contributions.\r\n\r\nYour donation to Freeform Portland can be tax-deductible! secure and easy one-time or monthly donations can be made via PayPal:\r\n\r\n[PayPal button]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Feel free to send a check, if  you''d like. Please make checks out to Freeform Portland and mail to:\r\nFreeform Portland\r\n801 N. Killingsworth St.\r\nPortland OR 97217</p>\r\nFreeform Portland will gratefully accept your donation of records, CDs and headphones in good working condition, plus office supplies, snacks, and more — please email TKTK@freeformportland.org to get in touch with a donations volunteer. You can also keep an eye out for the donation jar at most KFFP events.\r\n\r\nThanks so much!', 'Donate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'donate', '', '', '2016-02-26 04:52:17', '2016-02-26 04:52:17', '', 0, 'http://beta.freeformportland.org/?page_id=32', 9, 'page', '', 0),
